flowRoot.flowPara: We assessed population genetic structure for 366 samples of S. sclerotiorum. The manuscript and all analyses were written in RMarkdown. These were stored on GitHub, and run on circle-ci with a dedicated docker container and archived on the Open Science Framework.
Analysis is re-run after any change to the source code
Results are saved and archived at the OSFramework
The Dockerfile is used to rebuild the analysis anywhere; including the cloud and your computer.
